Title: The Pie
Plot: Jerry can't believe that his girlfriend won't share a piece of pie with him. There is a mannequin at a store that looks like Elaine and she wants to know where it came from. George is interested in a suit that he makes an enemy over. Kramer has an itch. George's new suit makes a noise.
GuestStars: Suzanne Snyder, Christine Dunford, Reni Santoni, Lane Davies, Mark Beltzman, Sunday Theodore, Sam Lloyd, Paul Mantee, Patricia Belcher, Pamela Mant, Bernard Hocke, Eamonn Roche, Robert Kino, Tony Edwards
